data.description: FHA assumable loan at 4.4% (buyer has to be FHA aprvd) Incredible and modern end-unit, 3-bedroom townhome in dreamy Beacon Hill, right on the edge of Columbia City. No HOA dues here! The impeccable attention to detail and quality finishes on this 4-star Built Green home will not disappoint! A chef's kitchen with Stainless appliances including a gas range, designer tile, high 10 ft ceilings, high-efficiency W/D, custom blinds, A/C mini splits, a tankless water heater, & Cat5 cabling. Assigned off-street parking, and a fully fenced side and back yard/patio. Easy commute with quick I5 and 90 access. Bus and light rail are just minutes away. Enjoy PCC, dining & entertainment of vibrant Columbia City & Hillman City down the street. Welcome Home!
